{"tid":581230,"cid":18,"subCid":6,"title":"分享下「地球監獄論」","createTime":"2018-03-05T07:12:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-18T15:40:55.000Z","uid":149978,"like":3,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"047d091840a894a563bb9aba750fc3508e8c8353","tid":581230,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T07:12:12.000Z","msg":"分享下地球監獄論<br />\n<br />\n大概意思係：地球係上帝或宇宙人去創造，人類和地球上的動物，都係宇宙或靈界犯了罪，要到地球呢個監獄受苦。<br />\n<br />\n地球本身的設計，係要犯人互相吃掉，互相折磨，互相斯殺，互相競爭。但又要互相合作，互相幫助，互愛，和平，先可以生存到。<br />\n<br />\n地球設計的目的，係要在宇宙或靈界犯左罪的人，來地球體驗「和平」、「智慧」、「愛」、「合作」的重要性，以及「暴力」、「自私」、「競爭」的可怕性。<br />\n<br />\n地球監獄論，這個假說，得到了一些「通靈者」通靈經驗報告所支持。比起宗教，更能受到邏輯上的考驗。但是，地球監獄論，仍然沒有實證支持，冇hard evidence."},{"pid":"6bb7a3ce76cedc709a319150f34b2838b34471b6","tid":581230,"uid":130901,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T07:19:14.000Z","msg":"覺得叫放逐適合d"},{"pid":"75551869d04c243a5cf8e0c18b90a10d52f55e04","tid":581230,"uid":65408,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T07:23:22.000Z","msg":"我認為監獄係為左懲罰罪犯同剥奪自由而設，如果被懲罰者跟本唔知自己係受緊罰有咩作用？"},{"pid":"16e0efe7b86d984d51f8eac3e5e4cc89daf189f7","tid":581230,"uid":149978,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T07:23:59.000Z","msg":"論壇<br />\n科學家：地球是大監獄<br />\n<a href=\"http://bbs.tianya.cn/m/post-218-9717-1.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbbs.tianya.cn%2Fm%2Fpost-218-9717-1.shtml&d=ZEo7vQ9fCHK54tDwjZR3fdU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=25a78e24\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bbs.tianya.cn/m/post-218-9717-1.shtml</a><br />\n<br />\nGOOGLE SEARCH<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com.hk/search?q=科學家+監獄地球&amp;oq=科學家+監獄地球\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com.hk%2Fsearch%3Fq%3D%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%B8%E5%AE%B6%2B%E7%9B%A3%E7%8D%84%E5%9C%B0%E7%90%83%26oq%3D%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%B8%E5%AE%B6%2B%E7%9B%A3%E7%8D%84%E5%9C%B0%E7%90%83&d=ZEo7vQ9fCHK54tDwjZR3fdU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=16cb853a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com.hk/search?q=科學家+監獄地球&amp;oq=科學家+監獄地球</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com.hk/search?q=地球是監獄&amp;oq=地球是監獄\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com.hk%2Fsearch%3Fq%3D%E5%9C%B0%E7%90%83%E6%98%AF%E7%9B%A3%E7%8D%84%26oq%3D%E5%9C%B0%E7%90%83%E6%98%AF%E7%9B%A3%E7%8D%84&d=ZEo7vQ9fCHK54tDwjZR3fdU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=a125cf26\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com.hk/search?q=地球是監獄&amp;oq=地球是監獄</a><br />\n<br />\n書：<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.books.com.tw/products/0010695910\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.books.com.tw%2Fproducts%2F0010695910&d=ZEo7vQ9fCHK54tDwjZR3fdU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=85efd45f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.books.com.tw/products/0010695910</a>"},{"pid":"9a35ea7094903e88912019992d94f58e6d24fb94","tid":581230,"uid":71446,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T07:32:48.000Z","msg":"咁點解要成功既人往往係不仁而不擇手段既人先做到?"},{"pid":"24e6a2e211255f5f921399bd83741be40f61c506","tid":581230,"uid":149978,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"75551869d04c243a5cf8e0c18b90a10d52f55e04","tid":581230,"uid":65408,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T07:23:22.000Z","msg":"我認為監獄係為左懲罰罪犯同剥奪自由而設，如果被懲罰者跟本唔知自己係受緊罰有咩作用？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T07:33:15.000Z","msg":"你肉體和大腦唔知，但你靈魂可能會知。或者出獄後，就會知道。"},{"pid":"591e984de37b869259dfab02d5364f476a47a898","tid":581230,"uid":149978,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"75551869d04c243a5cf8e0c18b90a10d52f55e04","tid":581230,"uid":65408,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T07:23:22.000Z","msg":"我認為監獄係為左懲罰罪犯同剥奪自由而設，如果被懲罰者跟本唔知自己係受緊罰有咩作用？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T07:35:12.000Z","msg":"可能離開左地球後，靈魂會記得返地球經歷。<br />\n<br />\n地球上的各大宗教都有咁暗示過。<br />\n<br />\n例如死後會有審判等。"},{"pid":"8e0e3463d10706f484a02c6da5e16ac3e8ef2d27","tid":581230,"uid":160738,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":